text: Feuille d'album may refer to: * Album leaf, a short musical composition also known as feuille d'album or feuillet d'album * Feuilles d'album, S.165 (Liszt), a piano piece by Franz Liszt *Feuillet d’album Op.81, a 4 hands piano piece by Camille Saint-Saëns * Feuille d'Album (short story), a short story by Katherine Mansfield
title: Feuille d'album
